# Evaluation System Instance
:EvaluationSystem_103001025 a guide:EvaluationSystem ;
    guide:evaluationDescription "The evaluation of this course is based on a progressive evaluation system (continuous evaluation), which grades the active participation of the student during the iterative development of an interactive project carried out in groups, following the human-centred design process." ;
    guide:hasEvaluationTrial :Trial_Assignment_5, :Trial_Assessment_7, :Trial_Assessment_10, :Trial_Assessment_13, :Trial_FinalExam .

